# Input

```css
a{color:/* before */red/* after */!important;}
a{color:red/* first *//* second */!important;}
a{color:red
/* own */
!important;}

```


# Formatted

```css
a {
	color:/* before */ red /* after */ !important;
}
a {
	color: red /* first */ /* second */ !important;
}
a {
	color: red /* own */ !important;
}

```
